sequenceDiagram
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant Database
participant AuthService
participant GoogleADK
participant LoadBalancer
participant Server

User->>Frontend: Login Request
Frontend->>Backend: Validate Credentials
Backend->>Database: Check Credentials
Database-->>Backend: Valid Credentials
Backend->>AuthService: Authenticate
AuthService-->>Backend: Auth Token
Backend-->>Frontend: Login Success
Frontend-->>User: Login Success

User->>Frontend: Upload CSV/Excel File
Frontend->>Backend: Upload File
Backend->>Database: Store File
Database-->>Backend: File Stored
Backend->>GoogleADK: Train Predictive Model
GoogleADK-->>Backend: Model Trained
Backend-->>Frontend: Model Trained
Frontend-->>User: Model Trained

User->>Frontend: View Dashboard
Frontend->>Backend: Get Real-time Analytics
Backend->>Database: Get Data
Database-->>Backend: Data
Backend-->>Frontend: Real-time Analytics
Frontend-->>User: Real-time Analytics

User->>Frontend: Request Report
Frontend->>Backend: Generate Report
Backend->>Database: Get Data
Database-->>Backend: Data
Backend-->>Frontend: Report
Frontend-->>User: Report

LoadBalancer->>Server: Route Request
Server->>Backend: Process Request
Backend->>Database: Get Data
Database-->>Backend: Data
Backend-->>Server: Response
Server-->>LoadBalancer: Response
LoadBalancer-->>User: Response